msgstr "否"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md
msgid ""
"Passed to Yuanrong `HeteroClient.enable_exclusive_connection`. Use `1` to"
" enable the exclusive connection mode when required by your deployment."
msgstr ""
"传递给元戎 `HeteroClient.enable_exclusive_connection`。当您的部署需要时，使用 `1` "
"来启用独占连接模式。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md
msgid "`DS_ENABLE_REMOTE_H2D`"
msgstr "`DS_ENABLE_REMOTE_H2D`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md
msgid ""
"Passed to Yuanrong `HeteroClient.enable_remote_h2d`. Use `1` only when "
"remote host-to-device transfer is enabled in your Datasystem deployment."
msgstr "传递给元戎 `HeteroClient.enable_remote_h2d`。仅当您的数据系统部署中启用了远程主机到设备传输时，才使用 `1`。"

